    //- Coyotes
    .flex-1of2
      .why.sky-blue.text-drk
        .icon.hockey-mask
        p The <a href="http://coyotes.nhl.com/">Arizona Coyotes</a> melt both the ice and our hearts.

    //- Meteor Crater
    .flex-1of2
      .why.tan.text-drk
        .icon.crater
        p <a href="http://www.barringercrater.com/">Barringer Crater</a> is “the best preserved meteorite crater on Earth.”

    //- Sunsets
    .flex-1of2
      .why.red.text-light
        .icon.sunset
        p You haven’t seen a sunset until you’ve seen an <a href="http://bit.ly/114BcbH">Arizona sunset</a>.

    //- Spring Training
    .flex-1of2
      .why.grey-light.text-drk
        .icon.baseball
        p Arizona hosts <a href="http://www.cactusleague.com/">15 Major League Baseball teams</a> for spring training.

    //- Biosphere
    .flex-1of2
      .why.navy-blue.text-light
        .icon.biosphere
        p <a href="http://www.b2science.org/">Biosphere 2</a> remains the largest closed ecosystem ever created.

    //- Ignite Phoenix
    .flex-1of2
      .why.umber.text-light
        .icon.match
        p <a href="http://www.ignitephoenix.com/">Ignite Phoenix</a> inspires and entertains with 5-minute talks.

    //- NAU
    .flex-1of2
      .why.grey-light.text-drk
        .icon.tshirt.nau
        p <a href="http://nau.edu/">Northern Arizona University’s</a> <a href="http://www.physics.nau.edu/">Department of Astronomy</a> ranked #2 nationally in 2011.

    //- Kartchner Caverns
    .flex-1of2
      .why.tan.text-drk
        .icon.kartchner-caverns
        p <a href="http://azstateparks.com/parks/kaca/index.html">Kartchner Caverns</a> features 2.5 miles of <a href="http://bit.ly/18Se9T0">pristine cave formations</a>.

    //- Arizona Cardinals
    .flex-1of2
      .why.sky-blue.text-drk
        .icon.football
        p The <a href="http://www.azcardinals.com/">Arizona Cardinals</a> are the oldest continuously run franchise in the NFL.

    //- Rodeo
    .flex-1of2
      .why.brown.text-light
        .icon.cowboy-hat
        p Payson is home to the <a href="http://www.paysonrimcountry.com/Activities/Rodeos/AugustDoinsRodeo.aspx">world’s oldest continuous rodeo</a>, started in the 1880s.

    //- Bone
    .flex-1of2
      .why.tan.text-drk
        .icon.fossil
        p <a href="http://www.nps.gov/pefo/index.htm">The Petrified Forest</a> has plant and animal fossils dating over 200 million years ago.

