        p The <a href="http://arizona.diamondbacks.mlb.com/">Arizona Diamondbacks</a> won the 2001 World Series in their fourth season as a team.

    //- Golf
    .flex-1of2
      .why.teal.text-light
        .icon.golfball
        p Arizona has over 300 <a href="http://www.worldgolf.com/courses/usa/arizona/">golf courses</a> and the weather to use them year-round.

    //- Hiking
    .flex-1of2
